# Verify Date Before Use

The "Today's date" in session metadata can be stale in long-running or resumed conversations. **Never trust it.**

Before writing any date-sensitive content (changelog entries, timestamps, version dates, comments):

1. Run `date` in the shell to get the actual current date
2. Use that date — not the session metadata date
